org.metastatic.sexp4j

Class Atom

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.metastatic.sexp4j.Atom
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, Expression

    public class Atom
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable, Expression
    An atom; that is, a sequence of bytes, with an optional display hint.
